{"tid":1421284,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"拎分機會! 一齊駁返好交通燈條線","createTime":"2019-08-06T07:38:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T10:57:30.000Z","uid":154978,"like":3,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c634002298e13c5c340f7415655b1d7340c888a8","tid":1421284,"uid":154978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:38:34.000Z","msg":"見班藍絲係咁攻擊嗰紅綠燈問題<br />\n<br />\n明白搞交通燈係幫到85罷工先做。老老實實，成本係要幾日先整得好，政府拖鐘更加耐。唔同港鐵，唔塞佢就即刻冇事<br />\n<br />\n揸車同行人都睇住支燈做人，見手足話無燈仲順，但一多車，就唔work，仲要幾日係咁<br />\n<br />\n你可以話等政府自己搞或派交通警，但今次真係剪得幾多咁<br />\n<br />\n同路人會明，但我地把握機會，主動得分更好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地係要拎得更加多人支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇電工牌"},{"pid":"21983465d3d33d3385350c3cd28fb444c6d59bbc","tid":1421284,"uid":270896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:41:02.000Z","msg":"唔係咁好喎好似<br />\n一陣去駁嗰班手足畀人當破壞拉咗咁點？"},{"pid":"14b1fa178db21a392c3e627e82441aab3abfc889","tid":1421284,"uid":154978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:42:55.000Z","msg":"計犯法就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗諗下"},{"pid":"e4b3a31e4b7062440b6ba806aeb1fda6db3ca572","tid":1421284,"uid":125582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77c33bb8bb227eba096272c8e21afafa28e21d9","tid":1421284,"uid":247341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T10:57:30.000Z","msg":"識唔識駁?電撚瓜你"}]}